      <lines>
        <dlgLine>
          <owner_ID>0</owner_ID>
          <text>I was talking to Craig and he is worried about Karen. He says that she is talking about aborting her child. Surely, with all that has gone lately, we can't throw away the gift of life so carelessly. </text>
          <defAppearChecks>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
