          </defAppearChecks>
          <onAppearChecks />
          <onLoadScripts />
        </dlgLine>
      </lines>
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>Yes, you're right. I will do my best to persuade her not to do it.</text>
          <def_link>1693</def_link>
          <auto_answer>false</auto_answer>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>It's not your problem or your body. Don't bring it up again with anyone. </text>
          <def_link>1694</def_link>
          <auto_answer>false</auto_answer>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>I won't allow her to have one or for anyone to help her. You have my word.</text>
          <def_link>1695</def_link>
          <auto_answer>false</auto_answer>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>It's Karen decision to make. I'm not getting involved.</text>
          <def_link>1694</def_link>
          <auto_answer>false</auto_answer>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>1692</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <lines>
        <dlgLine>
          <owner_ID>0</owner_ID>
          <text>I'd rather you forbid her, for the father's sake. This shouldn't even be up for discussion. Clearly, this is a blessing after so much tragedy. </text>
          <defAppearChecks>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
            <boolean>false</boolean>
