      <UID>1693</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <lines>
        <dlgLine>
          <owner_ID>0</owner_ID>
          <text>I see, so you're going to let her go ahead with this. I didn't expect this. It's going to be very difficult to support you with this in the back of my mind. Now, I will pray for Karen to find the strength to keep the child. </text>
